Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.62,0:00:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有證人在場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.59,0:00:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是... 不認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.05,0:00:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都說到這種地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 這張卡片放在了比我原來埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.93,0:00:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學為甚麼要選她做妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.76,0:00:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣沒甚麼特點的平凡學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她與祥子同學一點也不相襯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.36,0:01:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.92,0:01:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.39,0:01:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.01,0:01:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒緩的行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.36,0:03:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}紅色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早醒來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先浮現在腦中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.33,0:03:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「今天是情人節」這個事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.54,0:03:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 鵜澤美冬從高中開始進入了莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.26,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 與其它的外部應試者稍微有點不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.02,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 我曾在莉莉安的幼兒園上過一陣學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起 祥子同學對我來說就已經是一種特殊的存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 友子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.62,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學擁有著與他人不同的某種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可說是天生而來的 某種令人難以接近的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.02,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是繪畫 還是跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學都不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳得真好 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.98,0:04:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使受到誇獎 她也並未與其它人變得更親近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.71,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂小孩子 就是會對擁有與自已不同氣質的人而感到敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於同班同學所投射過來的驚奇的目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.97,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學毫不在意地只以沉鬱的表情無視掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學在無言地戰鬥著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.20,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為同班同學某句無心的話 她開始換乘班車來上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是讓車送到離自已家最近的候車點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從那裡乘上班車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了這種費勁的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而平凡的我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.67,0:05:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不可遏制地追尋著\N那樣的祥子同學在平常的點點滴滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那份幸福並未持續多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父親的調職決定後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也即將離開莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就不能再看到祥子同學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.61,0:05:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我 也並非是覺得與祥子同學分別很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.63,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因無法再看到祥子同學\n而感覺到深深的遺憾而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.94,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～ 是血 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快叫老師來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.17,0:06:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在幹甚麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為不聽老師的囑咐才會受到懲罰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.24,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了在從鞦韆上跌下來前\N所看到的祥子同學那不愉快的表情的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為站著盪鞦韆是被規章所禁止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給你了 我另外多帶了一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與祥子同學的對話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從別人那裡得到甚麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 到了我離開幼兒園的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了送給你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 媽媽叫我要送還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說這是謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.86,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請替我向美冬的媽媽說聲謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.66,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我第一次從祥子同學\n的嘴裡聽到自已名字的瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.22,0:07:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是永別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會再回到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會再回到她的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年後 我回到了莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大後的祥子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.84,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是如同聖母瑪莉亞一般優雅而恬靜的女性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我急切地期盼著再會的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在哪裡見過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學 老師在叫你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能暫時失陪一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.09,0:08:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.92,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻 我充份地明白了人不是那麼容易改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.97,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她仍舊是全身洋盈著讓他人無法接近的威嚴感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣毫無特點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連印象也沒法讓她留下的平凡的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與她之間的距離感與十年前完全沒有變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.60,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是眾多的同班同學中的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.08,0:09:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 她成了紅薔薇的花蕾的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了離我更遠的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.18,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 我也因回到了\N能注視著祥子同學的生活而感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年能交給她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概還是交不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為去年的情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的巧克力也沒有接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.52,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 我不能接受這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有接受的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有接受的理由也許就能讓她接受了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那時一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了今天的尋寶活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要去將卡片藏在某處！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我壓抑不住自已的好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 祥子同學的紅色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.29,0:11:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花蕾們到底把卡片藏在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是薔薇館最可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.51,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不會找到祥子同學的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的卡片就像是一張王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.37,0:11:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要怎麼使用全看我的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.07,0:11:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是今天的值日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.77,0:11:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大森老師不是說過\N「立刻來理科準備室取第五節課要用的資料」嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一點兒資料我一個人就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.81,0:12:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.99,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到祥子同學的臉後 我變得害怕起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.43,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把偷偷先找到的卡片\n若無其事地拿到薔薇館去的膽量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在放回去的話 還來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好不容易才到手的卡片卻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.85,0:12:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅 白 黃的卡片將分別藏在校內的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制時間是一小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到卡片後 請帶回到作為本部的薔薇館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.38,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就可獲贈\N作為附加獎的與花蕾們的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我猶豫的時候 尋寶活動開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢啊 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為想要的東西就擺在眼前 竟未做多想就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.36,0:13:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 終於理解到自已所做所為的嚴重性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須把它放回原來的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 即使還了回去 像這種地方一定不會有人來找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此 我也沒資格就這樣拿著它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.25,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要祥子同學回頭看看我而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.49,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為不聽老師的囑咐才會受到懲罰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受到懲罰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與這張紅色卡片一起 被關在了這個古舊的溫室裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.05,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 好像嚇到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是來這裡找卡片嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.02,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福澤祐巳同學 是祥子同學所選的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.09,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 祥子同學將隱藏的地點告訴了祐巳同學呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話 我也能稍微安心一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那些一無所知地尋找祥子同學卡片的人來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學跟我一樣罪孽深重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是狗一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.58,0:14:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 像這樣拼命地 幹勁十足地掘著土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說祐巳同學...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想卡片應該就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼認真的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.39,0:14:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學果然是靠自已的力量找到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話 請用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼挖也無法在那裡找到卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.19,0:15:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但越是把這一結局往後拖延\n我就越覺得自已變得污穢似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法再忍耐著看下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那裡沒有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.10,0:15:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我說晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我剛才也挖掘過那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼會認為卡片在那裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.01,0:15:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然事前沒有被告知過 那麼祐巳同學是怎麼找到這裡來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個薔薇就叫做紅薔薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是紅薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同祥子同學的分身般的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.93,0:15:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以祥子同學才會將卡片藏在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.51,0:15:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 只有祐巳同學察覺到了這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全地輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.80,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此的接近 我卻完全未察覺到這種花的含義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到4點40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加活動的同學們請立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動結束了 請立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.86,0:16:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就在這裡分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學為甚麼會選擇她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她與祥子同學一點也不相襯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我擅自地那樣認定著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但通過今天的事我明白了一些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學擁有著我所沒有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而祥子同學發現了這些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.77,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同學的確有看人的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到「中」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會無一例外地獲贈與我的半天約會權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.05,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 那個 這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.97,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.89,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.79,0:17:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 那麼這周的周日如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你想去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去祐巳想去的地方就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓我先想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會期待著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學入學考試做得還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 今天的估計不大好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你反倒是相當的愉快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.09,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為托了尋寶活動的福 我的願望實現了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.42,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是那個「在畢業之前 我想看看薔薇館裡普通學生們喧鬧的樣子」嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.09,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 今天是我到目前為止的人生中最好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.45,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我能去您家裡拜訪您嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.47,0:18:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西想交給您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要把卡片藏在那麼奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.26,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把卡片夾在「江戶的物價」甚麼的書間 太難明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 生氣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種話等一會兒再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我也會去由乃的家裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 姐姐 等會兒再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也是夾心巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是特意送到家裡來的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.23,0:19:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是慣例的手製品了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 從靜那裡得到了酒心巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃點暖暖身體嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在某些地方真是有點遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.39,0:19:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓我拿了專為姐姐而做的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜大人會是一種甚麼心情呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.98,0:19:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 又給我上了一堂課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得很自大的樣子真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.15,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有一個懂事的妹妹我真是幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.63,0:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能輕鬆坦然地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.02,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 請不要這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.85,0:20:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果姐姐不在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天 志摩子也會成為二年級生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生入學後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.62,0:20:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再察覺時 我的離開也就變得很平常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不覺得會是那麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大理石花紋巧克力蛋糕 真是非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.69,0:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.18,0:21:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有關本周日的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 能請你先回教室嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.45,0:21:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 祥子同學的縫紉箱就先放在我這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拜託你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會先放在祥子同學的桌上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟姐姐慢慢地談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 周日的事是？
